name: The Day We've All Been Waiting For - Variant 01
description: Accidental glitch video export when producing the original piece, There was a beauty to this unexpected result in the creative process that needed to be honored. Perhaps it was the ghost of Hal Finney in the machine coming through, reminding us all to be strong and HODL through all the static noise going on around us.
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art. SuperRare's smart contract platform allows artists to release limited-edition digital artwork tracked on the blockchain, making the pieces rare, verified, and collectible. Filter the crypto art world's best selling works by artist name, creation type, and year of birth on OpenSea.
